scene.message:
Nanjo: Honestly, you lot are{nl}
so slow.{wait_fr:32} Be brisk in your{nl}
movements, like me!{wait_fr:32} As they{nl}
say, youth fades fast.{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: What is it, {ctl0f:1}!{nl}
Do you need something?!{nl}
If not, go away!!!{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: That Nanjo jerk really{nl}
ticks me off~ Someday I'll{nl}
get some dirt on him.{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Young master~!{wait_fr:21}{nl}
Get it? Young master~?{wait_fr:21}{nl}
Bffft{wait_fr:32} this one's a winner~!{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: That old man Yamaoka{nl}
really does dote on Nanjo,{nl}
huh.{waitkey}{ret}

Student: A weird old man was{nl}
standing by the school gate{nl}
earlier. Creepy, huh.{waitkey}{ret}

Student: Hey, hey, isn't{nl}
Nanjo kind of scary? Cool, or{nl}
rather, so coolheaded.{waitkey}{ret}
